aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724537b164b22be6c7e810c21d4971846817e249","tid":2186000,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"返夠一年等佢加埋人工就走"},{"pid":"44e89895ff516480f4841bd58fbdf8b5baaf5838","tid":2186000,"uid":67294,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"Fg搵工甚實真係唔難<br />\n因為你係公司人工支出最低果個，公司要請你都唔洗考慮啲乜<br />\n<br />\n重要反而係你點知份工岩你做"},{"pid":"5e3fbd2493a41f828390c9a48c6204b38a74a722","tid":2186000,"uid":19640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:13:44.000Z","msg":"第一份工係咁 就算做皇帝都想轉工<br />\n過兩年你會後悔點解當初轉工<br />\n香港地份份工都鳩 唔會有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfce3213bfd4f4ab461de0285527d16f25680885","tid":2186000,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"我，有第個offer，過兩個禮拜辭職，仲要做多個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ba20a658cb768580f8009eed6d4ae0ce4e1516","tid":2186000,"uid":170091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"襯後生，我諗都係唔啱揾到啱算。第一份工應該點都有啲火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無謂做到自己頹哂算"},{"pid":"d6fd47b45cf2295f47859fdc283ae644e2d873a3","tid":2186000,"uid":131968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T06:01:47.000Z","msg":"想轉, 覺得自己係公司冇用, 冇咩野做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申已經做左一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fe01a5380fb30b318ddc6da9681848e3994a77","tid":2186000,"uid":128290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60d554691ddb1d43ddb4e8bd3d0af61d7ca70c67","tid":2186000,"uid":170091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:33:56.000Z","msg":"如題&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n到底咩原因會令到大家下定決心唔做？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:16:52.000Z","msg":"走<br />\n<br />\n利申: 上一份工 人工同福利比宜家好"},{"pid":"e0e1e38434c4777bddbc29255222375f96f3df1d","tid":2186000,"uid":190141,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:21:21.000Z","msg":"返左個半月之後將我丟黎丟去<br />\n兩星期內轉左4個返工地點 最後仲要過海<br />\n直接交信走人 由有諗頭到交信都只係幾個鐘內既事<br />\n<br />\n都係果句啦 even 你30歲先出黎做野 60歲退休 你都要做成30年野 唔好話幾個月 唔做野一年都唔覺有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93254d271f8d1c589915e44216d9cec19af0e5b4","tid":2186000,"uid":116879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"返左半個月已經想辭職"}]}